Model Z

Designed to be the last car you'll ever buy, Model Z can drive 400 miles on a single gallon of milk while costing only 35 human souls before incentives.

text_264596390.text:
Model Q & Model Z

The Model Q is our premium automobile. It can drive further, go faster, and costs way, way more money. It's the least unsafe form of transportation we've ever created. Unlike some other cars in its class, the constant tortured screaming from the speakers is barely audible.

The Model Z is constructed much more shoddily. Just as Z comes after Q in the alphabet, our Model Z customers come after Model Q customers in terms of our service commitment to them. You get what you pay for.
